{"tid":2153814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果頭版開放留言　港人撐牆半日爆額 呼籲大家踴躍支持 填滿成份蘋果","createTime":"2020-08-12T18:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T23:58:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ccd0be51cc88f932317c9f9328f5a588e2cb412","tid":2153814,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:44:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/CTV44EQ77BVSDJKHKKBNEEY4ME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FCTV44EQ77BVSDJKHKKBNEEY4ME%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7Tv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=d3c91d83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FCTV44EQ77BVSDJKHKKBNEEY4ME%2F&h=35934fef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/CTV44EQ77BVSDJKHKKBNEEY4ME/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》fb專頁昨傍晚亦宣佈，「多謝大家支持，頭版蘋果連儂牆轉眼已經集氣爆棚」，並指將會開放《蘋果》其他內頁供有意者留言，「希望將大家嘅心聲喺蘋果遍地開花，填滿成份蘋果！」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》營業部表示，由昨早10時許推出計劃，不消大半日已「撐爆咗頭版」，又指直到昨晚已有70多人登記，當中最多人選擇留言字句是「香港人撐住！蘋果人撐住！」。過去《蘋果》亦曾推出同類計劃，最終有兩版連儂牆，相信今次計劃會多於兩版，呼籲大家踴躍支持。"},{"pid":"1a89ffb2a2abdecdb347d45162f01984568af9c4","tid":2153814,"uid":273294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f337b4f2318a5b0688e222293875ddfe97eb39","tid":2153814,"uid":273294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YTuuKYw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYTuuKYw.jpg&h=38724644&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ee411883271297c5f5be96792aa9ba67e3a55c9","tid":2153814,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a89ffb2a2abdecdb347d45162f01984568af9c4","tid":2153814,"u